name: Pea Pod Necklace... Sterling and Freshwater Pearls
description:
This is perfect for you and your wedding party. I have also had people get it for family, mother and sisters. I can put in as many/little pearls as you would like.

I started with heavy gauge wire and formed the pea pod shape. I then wire wrapped 6mm white freshwater pearls into the pea pod. I attached the pendant to sterling chain. I will custom make this necklace per order. You can customize color of pearls and length of the necklace.

All jewelry is shipped in a recycled craft paper box, perfect for gift giving. Sizes, colors, stones, ear wires, shapes... can all be customized. Email me to inquire. Thanks for stopping by!

name: Initial Necklace... custom order, sterling and birthstones
description:
I will create this necklace custom for you. I start with sterling blanks and stamp the letter of your choice. I then darken the letter for contrast. I will wire wrap the stones/crystals of you choice to dangle. They are 1/2" long. You can pick the style of sterling chain... box, ball, cable, etc. Please allow 2 weeks for delivery.

All jewelry is shipped in a recycled kraft paper box, perfect for gift giving. Sizes, colors, stones, ear wires, shapes... can all be customized. Email me to inquire. Thanks for stopping by!

name: Mixed Fabric Poppy Bobby Pin
description:
Super cute affordable bobby pins to jazz up any outfit. I started with green and gold Asian printed fabrics and singed to prevent fraying. I wire wrapped a purple rice shaped freshwater pearl to the center. The flower is about 1 1/2" X 1 1/4" and wire wrapped to a bobby pin.

All jewelry is shipped in a recycled craft paper box, perfect for gift giving. Sizes, colors, stones, ear wires, shapes... can all be customized. Email me to inquire. Thanks for stopping by!

name: Quilted Basket Necklace... Sterling and Freshwater Pearls
description:
This is one of my favorite styles. I started with sterling wire that I formed into a rectangle shape. I then hand wrap a mixture of freshwater pearls into it. I placed one small pearl dangle on the side. The necklace is composed of wire wrapped 8mm nugget shaped white freshwater pearls. The closure is a handmade hook and eye clasp. The necklace is almost 17 1/4" long. All metals are sterling silver.

All jewelry is shipped in a recycled kraft paper box, perfect for gift giving. Sizes, colors, stones, ear wires, shapes... can all be customized. Email me to inquire. Thanks for stopping by!
